OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength not
OL,4,Cweakness': London MPs on PM's
OL,5,Cimmigration crackdown
OL,7,FSimon Harris talks to members of the
OL,8,FBangladeshi community as MPs speak out
OL,9,Fon Labour's new immigration policy
OL,11,FMayor Sir Sadiq Khan has vowed to
OL,12,F'talk up the benefits of migration'
OL,13,Famid a backlash over the government's
OL,14,Fproposed crackdown.
OL,16,FPrime minister Sir Keir Starmer used a
OL,17,FDowning Street announcement to unveil
OL,18,Fnew curbs and insist newcomers to the
OL,19,FUK must learn English.
