OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength not
OL,4,Cweakness': London MPs on PM's
OL,5,Cimmigration crackdown
OL,7,FBut left-wing London MP John McDonnell
OL,8,Fsuggested Starmer's speech had echoes
OL,9,Fof Enoch Powell - the Tory politician
OL,10,Fwhose 'rivers of blood' speech sparked
OL,11,Foutrage.
OL,13,FStarmer told journalists: "When people
OL,14,Fcome to our country, they should also
OL,15,Fcommit to integration, to learning our
OL,16,Flanguage.
OL,18,F"In a diverse nation like ours - and I
OL,19,Fcelebrate that - these rules become
OL,20,Feven more important. Without them we
OL,21,Frisk becoming an island of strangers"
