OL,7,FHayes & Harlington MP McDonnell -
OL,8,Fcurrently suspended by Labour - used a
OL,9,FCommons question to Home Secretary
OL,10,FYvette Cooper to criticise Starmer.
OL,12,FHe asked: "When the prime minister
OL,13,Freferred to an island of strangers,
OL,14,Freflecting the language of Enoch
OL,15,FPowell, does he realise how shockingly
OL,16,Fdivisive that could be?"
