OL,8,Fin 1968 included an inflammatory
OL,9,Fwarning: "In 15 or 20 years time, the
OL,10,Fblack man will have the whip hand over
OL,11,Fthe white man".
OL,13,FBackbench London Labour MPs also
OL,14,Ftrumpeted the diversity of their
OL,15,Fconstituencies in an apparent shot
OL,16,Facross the government's bows.
