OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength not
OL,4,Cweakness': London MPs on PM's
OL,5,Cimmigration crackdown
OL,7,FKhan declined to openly criticise
OL,8,Fministers but told ITV News: "I'm
OL,9,Fquite clear, both as the mayor of
OL,10,FLondon and as a citizen of this great
OL,11,Fcity, I can see the benefits on a
OL,12,Fdaily basis, economically, socially
OL,13,Fand culturally of successive waves of
OL,14,Flegal migration."
OL,16,FHe added: "As long as I'm mayor I'll
OL,17,Fbe celebrating our diversity as a
OL,18,Fstrength not a weakness".
