OL,3,C'Diversity is a strength not
OL,4,Cweakness': London MPs on PM's
OL,5,Cimmigration crackdown
OL,7,FEast London restaurant owner Niaz Caan
OL,8,Fsaid he feared the new visa rules
OL,9,Fcould cause staff shortages in curry
OL,10,Fhouse kitchens.
OL,12,FMr Caan, executive chef at Spice City
OL,13,Fin Whitechapel's Brick Lane called on
OL,14,Fthe mayor to take a tougher stand
OL,15,Fagainst ministers.
OL,17,FHe said: "He needs to speak up, not
OL,18,Fonly on the cultural element...but
OL,19,Falso from an economic point of view,
OL,20,Fin that you need migrants to fill the
OL,21,Fgaps."
